      • loadAssetIntoView

        public void loadAssetIntoView(View view)
        Loads an asset into a view. Loads an asset into a view of the appropriate type. For strings, this must be an instance of TextView. For images, it must be an instance of ImageView.
        Parameters:
        view - The view in which to place the asset.

      • getAssetView

        public View getAssetView(Context context)
        Constructs a view containing the asset. Constructs and loads an asset into a view of the appropriate type. For strings, this returns an instance of TextView. For images, it returns an instance of ImageView.
        Parameters:
        context - The current activity context.
        Returns:
        The view for the asset.
